circumstances: Hazel Fisher left home after an argument and was last seen near a resort.

After leaving home during an argument, Hazel Fisher was last seen heading towards music lessons. A friend and colleague reported her missing from Acre Drive, Glasgow, G20 0TR. She was later traced by police at an address on Belsyde Avenue, Glasgow, G15 6AR.
